name: Men's & Women's COR Wear-Anywhere Shirt
description:
Fitted and super soft, share your love of obstacle events and Colorado with this wear-anywhere Vintage Blue or Black tee! The Vintage Black has variations making it look dark, dark gray. 
50% Polyester 25% Cotton 25% Rayon. 
Pre-shrunk, Extremely soft, comfortable, and stretchy.

* The Fit for Guys: Athletic/Modern Fit, true to size
* The Fit for Women: This is a unisex shirt, so it is slightly looser than pic (fitted but not tight). Size small looks great on most!

name: Colorado Strong COR Team Shirt
description:
Stand out in this yellow or blue Dryblend shirt. DryBlend Moisture Wicking Fabric, Preshrunk Jersey knit 
50% Cotton / 50% DryBlend Polyester Jersey
Sizes go up past XXL, let us know if you need more info.

Have a closet full of race swag? Us too! 
Here's how this shirt compares:
* Softness: above average
* You will want to wear this: to the gym and races
* The Fit: Classic, so most women will want a small or medium and taller or bigger guys will want to go larger.

name: Men's & Women's COR Hoodies
description:
HEAVYWEIGHT HOODIE: The soft, warm, go-to layer for the winter. Cotton/Polyester fleece blend. Royal Blue color. 
* Fit: Loose and comfy. Men's sizing 

TRIBLEND JERSEY HOODIE:
The long-sleeve, fitted, tri-blend hoodie is Vintage Black, so a dark gray with some variations. Unisex sizing, Pre-shrunk, Extremely soft, comfortable and stretchy. 
* Fit: It is an Athletic/Modern Fit, so for guys it will be true to size but they may want size larger for layering. Perfect for women who want more wiggle room than the burnout. 

WOMEN'S BURNOUT HOODIE: This is currently on Back Order.
